    <modellingAndValidation>
      <representativeness systemModelId="290c1f85-4cc4-4fa1-b0c8-2cb7f4276dce">
        <systemModelName xml:lang="en">Allocation, cut-off by classification</systemModelName>
        <extrapolations xml:lang="en">Since the Brazilian matrix is completely interconnected, it is not possible to know the destination of the imported electricity, since it can go anywhere in the country, so the geographic proximity was considered to assign this import to the Southern region. The Annual Production Volume is estimated considering the fraction of electricity imported from Paraguai to the total electricity imported by Brazil. Fractions are available in: &lt;http://www2.aneel.gov.br/aplicacoes/capacidadebrasil/OperacaoCapacidadeBrasil.cfm&gt; Accessed in 04-2018</extrapolations>
      </representativeness>
